rows.label: tlk47300162_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Good to have you back, Rex! You
know we're all proper proud of you.
What brings you back so soon?

rows.label: tlk47300162_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The Village Guardian? Well, I'd be
careful if I were you.

rows.label: tlk47300162_02_msg0003
rows.name:
There're some ridiculously strong
monsters roaming around them parts.
But I'm sure you're capable enough.

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Monsters have never shown up here.
I don't even want to imagine things
lurking beneath the village...

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0101
rows.name:

Guardian, you'd better be careful.
